{"tid":1751622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依個警員講d野不無道理","createTime":"2019-11-24T17:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T00:34:11.000Z","uid":74642,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"847bc1fae37dc4a466675df77806a89d9d6ab342","tid":1751622,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"// 警員晚上在理大外圍開咪，向留守校園的人說：「我真係覺得你哋好垃圾，做又做唔掂、做又做唔好。我睇你哋唔起呀，唔係因為我同你政見、立場唔同，係因為你哋做人冇原則、冇底線、冇承擔、冇責任感，同埋冇腦啊。」<br />\n<br />\n該警員稱，這幾個月發現香港受過多年免費教育的人，智商、分析、邏輯能力比沒受過教育的人更低，指董先生已承認教育政策失敗，教咗一班咁嘅人出嚟，<span style=\"color: red;\">「唉！自己懾高枕頭再諗一諗啦！唔好淨係收埋自己鍾意睇嗰啲嘢，接觸下出面多啲人嘅諗法，擴闊下自己嘅眼光，睇一睇其他人嘅文章，你會發現，原來你係錯得好緊要㗎！」</span>。警員又叫留守者，接觸多些外邊人的想法、擴闊自己眼光」<span style=\"color: red;\">。「你哋真係喺度發緊夢架，我話你聽，呢個夢好快醒，你哋全部要承擔之前錯誤所帶來嘅惡果」。</span><br />\n<br />\n警員又提及留守者要食「冰冰冷冷的生命麵包」，但警察收工後可以到深圳食海底撈、可以飲冰凍啤酒，「而你哋就繼續喺度食生命麵包......通常基層拾荒者老人家食，我覺得好可憐。」// <br />\n<br />\n資料來源：眾新聞<br />\n<br />\n有種責任 👇🏻請追蹤/follow👇🏻<br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKOneResp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKOneResp&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJb7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=e154f214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKOneResp</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkoneresp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkoneresp&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJb7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=5ccc48dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkoneresp</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港 #香港加油 #hongkong #五大訴求缺一不可 #光復香港時代革命 #香港人 #fightforfreedom #standwithhongkong #文宣 #有種責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來狗話係同d狗講架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">恭喜區選報捷，但我地未贏<br />\n香港人，繼續反抗！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ac0df3c7a68d2d6c32091baffa15335ba25dd0c","tid":1751622,"uid":74642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:49:42.000Z","msg":"等睇被清算<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Condom仔</span>"},{"pid":"0417b1abc4986f532ced700948bbb8fe78c96d7d","tid":1751622,"uid":12712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"仲有民意逆轉個阿sir去左邊？"},{"pid":"49fbe99d233f18456c5664da14340b588f2f2d39","tid":1751622,"uid":74642,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:55:02.000Z","msg":"又指留守者薪水低、破壞中大及理大，誣衊他們「妒忌警察」，甚至稱留守者「憎人富貴嫌人貧」，更提到11.24區議會選舉，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「你哋睇下24號嘅投票結果會係點！民意逆轉！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n留名恥笑"},{"pid":"349e0ad44441ed22bd3d7f8ad1d18d5582dd8b96","tid":1751622,"uid":9759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"仲有個地鐵綠曱甴話<br />\n而家市民支持我地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bcb82ad6101bce669a1535dee374f79c17a2f3","tid":1751622,"uid":245409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"如果贏既話開咪講返同一段野比佢地聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c077ec4e306912e3ff64f71aa50b03b62ea5900","tid":1751622,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:58:39.000Z","msg":"真係以為自己的世界代表全部人<br />\n個呀sir會唔會接受唔倒現實？"},{"pid":"8b9c7e93576be3f5bfa3808f235780bd894d316e","tid":1751622,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:17:39.000Z","msg":"一齊回顧下"},{"pid":"6a1c01fae8e02d3e7a15afca9a016963b15910a9","tid":1751622,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}